  "prompt": "How do you remove your Gmail Profile picture?",
  "response": "To remove your Gmail profile picture, follow these steps:\n\n1. Open Gmail in your web browser\n\n2. Click on the profile picture/icon in the top right corner of the screen\n\n3. Click \"Manage your Google Account\"\n\n4. Select the \"Personal info\" tab on the left side\n\n5. Click on your current profile picture\n\n6. Click the \"Remove\" button\n\n7. Confirm that you want to remove the picture\n\nAfter completing these steps, your profile picture will be deleted and will revert to a generic Google account icon.",
